						Continue Reading
					&lt;/a&gt;
				</description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 12 Aug 2010 16:53:24 +0800</pubDate>
				<link>http://chenjun.com/blog/2010/08/n97-stolen-by-a-uighur-at-taiyuan-railway-station.html</link>
				<guid isPermaLink="true">http://chenjun.com/blog/2010/08/n97-stolen-by-a-uighur-at-taiyuan-railway-station.html</guid>
			</item>
		
